problem:
How many rectangles are there whose four vertices are points on this grid? [asy]
size(50);
dot((0,0));
dot((5,0));
dot((10,0));
dot((0,5));
dot((0,10));
dot((5,5));
dot((5,10));
dot((10,5));
dot((10,10));
[/asy]

